data.description: Welcome to your forever home in highly desired lake neighborhood in Thornwood. Situated on a 1 ACRE OF LAND semi-wooded lot! Newly renovated with the perfect combination of modern and barn style. A farmhouse sink, and barn doors that lead to a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances Outside you'll find a huge fenced backyard ready for your future gatherings. NO HOA !!  New roof and interior paint, move-in ready with a peace of mind. This home offers a peaceful suburban setting while still having easy access to amenities, shopping, schools, etc. Schedule your showing now!
